bug.short_desc: Invalid behavior of justify center on numbered/unordered lists

long_desc.thetext:
if i add a numbered/unordered list to the htmlarea and then pressing the justify center button only the text inside each list element is justified correctly. The numbers or bullets are still on the left side of the document.
can be reproduce on IE7 and less, Chrome and FF. IE8 works.
Discontinued support for htmlarea in the framework, set all open issues to WONTFIX. Still available as a contribution acc. to bug #7918 .
